  <div class="content">

    
    
            
                    <a href="/content/january-2014-issue-linux-journal-security" class="imagecache imagecache-teaser imagecache-linked imagecache-teaser_linked"></a>        
        


Lapsang Souchong!

<p>
Back when we were kids, "security" meant little more than having a secret
password to keep little siblings out of the treehouse.<span class="read-more"><a href="/content/january-2014-issue-linux-journal-security"> more>></a></span></p>
