      <h2 class="title">
      <a href="/content/using-open-source-framework-catch-bad-guy" title="Government: Using an Open Source Framework to Catch the Bad Guy">Government: Using an Open Source Framework to Catch the Bad Guy</a>
    </h2>
  
  

  
